
### `.devcontainer/devcontainer.json` — this makes it ONE CLICK
```json
{
  "name": "Remote Browser",
  "image": "mcr.microsoft.com/devcontainers/base:ubuntu",
  "forwardPorts": [6080],
  "portsAttributes": {
    "6080": {
      "label": "Remote Browser",
      "onAutoForward": "openBrowser"
    }
  },
  "postStartCommand": "bash start.sh"
}
